'''''Ayiram Muthangal''''' is a [[1982 in film|1982]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by Annakkili S.Devarajan for Thirupur Mani. The film stars [[Sivakumar]], [[Radha (actress)|Radha]] and Sivachandran in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Ayiram Muthangal LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/118/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-05-01|}}</ref>

